# AIDevBlogGen — Environment Variables
#
# LLM calls use GitHub Copilot SDK. Auth is automatic via:
#   - GITHUB_TOKEN env var (set by GitHub Actions, or manually)
#   - `gh auth token` (if GITHUB_TOKEN is not set — requires gh CLI login)
#
# No API keys needed for LLM — Copilot handles auth.

# ── LLM Models (optional — code defaults used if not set) ────────────────────
# LLM_MODEL: cheap model (default: claude-haiku-4.5)
# LLM_MODEL_HEAVY: premium model for spotlight posts (default: claude-opus-4.6)
# For testing, set both to gpt-4.1 (0 premium requests):
# LLM_MODEL=gpt-4.1
# LLM_MODEL_HEAVY=gpt-4.1

# ── GITHUB_TOKEN (optional — only needed outside GitHub Actions) ─────────────
# If not set, falls back to `gh auth token` (requires `gh auth login`)
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...
